e reading of Gualtherus' second edition, only confuses the issue, rather than providing certainty (e.g. the painting of an A in line 3 appears to be without foundation on the stone). The text would appear to be of early (i.e. Augustan) date, reflecting construction of the aqueduct around the foundation of the Roman colonia.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":319,"html":320},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Gualtherus 1624 273 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002388\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002388\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Gualtherus 1624 [1625] \u003Ca href=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/item/buchseite/310975\" target=\"_blank\">335\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Mommsen 1883 \u003Ca href=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/item/buchseite/650753\" target=\"_blank\">6999\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Lagona 1964 84-85 tav.25.3 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001437\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001437\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Coarelli and Torelli 1984 334 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002073\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002073\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1988 44 n.216 tav.14 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Belvedere 1988 378 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001429\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001429\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Wilson 1988 125 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001430\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscription